      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rr-dat-max           to   w-edt-dat-dat          .
           perform   edt-dat-fmt-000      thru edt-dat-fmt-999        .
           move      w-edt-dat-edt        to   w-vsy-hdr-dat          .
       stp-srt-inp-aaa-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record [hpo] per la testata        *
