      *
           move      rr-fil-pos           to   rf-hpo-pth-pos         .
           move      00000                to   rf-hpo-prg-inp         .
      *
           move      rr-dat-min           to   rf-hpo-dat-min         .
           move      rr-dat-max           to   rf-hpo-dat-max         .
           move      spaces               to   rf-hpo-flg-inv         .
      *
           move      w-vsy-hdr            to   rf-hpo-dat-pos         .
           move      spaces               to   rf-hpo-alx-exp         .
       stp-srt-inp-aaa-600.
