      *                      * Numero progressivo                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   srt-prg-inp            .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Composizione dati                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Record [hpo]                            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-hpo               to   srt-rec-hpo            .
       stp-srt-inp-aaa-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
