           move      09                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      w-vsy-dtl-qty        to   w-all-str-alf          .
           perform   all-str-adx-000      thru all-str-adx-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-vsy-dtl-qty          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
