           move      0002                 to   d-vun-mag-tip-val      .
           move      rr-dat-min           to   d-vun-mag-dat-val      .
           move      01                   to   d-vun-mag-tip-mag      .
           move      rf-bir-num-pro       to   d-vun-mag-num-mag      .
           move      "pgm/mag/prg/obj/pmag300v"
